      "rationale": "NIH and RH index are the standard hemolysis metrics per ASTM F1841 and ISO 10993-4. Direct mechanistic link between shear stress exposure and RBC damage established via Giersiepen power-law model. RH < 1 acceptance criterion directly maps to non-inferiority vs predicate device."
