    "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/decision/dr-cou1-cpb-accepted",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per approved MRL 2 assessment plan. Mesh GCI of 3.1% and experimental agreement within 1σ across all five validation operating points provide sufficient confidence that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied at all evaluated conditions. Model credibility is sufficient for the intended regulatory submission supporting 510(k) clearance.",
